  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Promoting better acess to basic services in the DRC (emphasis on education)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project is part of the education PIP00200. It will address the issue of user fees for healcare as well as the quality of primary education school in Kinshasa through improving the learning and teaching processes, empowering communities, and identifying strategies that can enhance learning for girls. All this will be well documented and accompanied by a thorough analysis of current policies and practice, which will support the push for policy change.</narrative>
  </description>
